{"prompt": "Design a dynamic e-commerce store for a gourmet chocolate shop. The aesthetic should incorporate a rich cocoa brown.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Gourmet Chocolate Delights</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #4A2C2A; /* Rich cocoa brown */\n            color: #F5EFE6; /* Creamy off-white for contrast */\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #6B4226; /* Slightly lighter brown for header */\n            color: #F5EFE6;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #F5EFE6;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            padding: 8px 15px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            background-color: #4A2C2A;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: rgba(107, 66, 38, 0.5); /* Semi-transparent brown overlay */\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #F5EFE6;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #F5EFE6;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .products {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 25px;\n        }\n        .product-card {\n            background-color: #6B4226;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .product-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n        .product-card img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .product-card h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #F5EFE6;\n        }\n        .product-card p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: rgba(245, 239, 230, 0.8);\n        }\n        .price {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #FFD700; /* Gold accent for price */\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .add-to-cart {\n            background-color: #A0522D; /* Sienna brown for button */\n            color: #F5EFE6;\n            border: none;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .add-to-cart:hover {\n            background-color: #8B4513; /* Darker sienna brown */\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            background-color: #6B4226;\n            color: #F5EFE6;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(74, 44, 42, 0.7), rgba(107, 66, 38, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x400/4A2C2A/F5EFE6?text=Gourmet+Chocolate'); /* Placeholder for a rich image */\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            color: #F5EFE6;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border-bottom: none;\n            color: #F5EFE6;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Gourmet Chocolate Delights</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <a href=\"#home\">Home</a>\n            <a href=\"#products\">Our Chocolates</a>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\" id=\"home\">\n        <h2>Indulge in Pure Bliss</h2>\n        <p>Discover handcrafted chocolates made with the finest cocoa beans, offering an unparalleled taste experience.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"products\">\n            <h2>Our Exquisite Chocolates</h2>\n            <div class=\"products\">\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/A0522D/F5EFE6?text=Dark+Chocolate+Truffles\" alt=\"Dark Chocolate Truffles\">\n                    <h3>Dark Chocolate Truffles</h3>\n                    <p>Rich, intense dark chocolate ganache enrobed in a delicate cocoa dusting.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$18.00</p>\n                    <button class=\"add-to-cart\">Add to Cart</button>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/8B4513/F5EFE6?text=Milk+Chocolate+Bark\" alt=\"Milk Chocolate Bark\">\n                    <h3>Milk Chocolate Bark</h3>\n                    <p>Creamy milk chocolate studded with toasted almonds and sea salt flakes.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$15.00</p>\n                    <button class=\"add-to-cart\">Add to Cart</button>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/6B4226/F5EFE6?text=White+Chocolate+Raspberry\" alt=\"White Chocolate Raspberry\">\n                    <h3>White Chocolate Raspberry</h3>\n                    <p>Velvety white chocolate swirled with tart raspberry pieces and crunchy freeze-dried raspberries.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$16.50</p>\n                    <button class=\"add-to-cart\">Add to Cart</button>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4A2C2A/F5EFE6?text=Spiced+Chili+Bar\" alt=\"Spiced Chili Bar\">\n                    <h3>Spiced Chili Bar</h3>\n                    <p>A bold blend of 70% dark chocolate infused with a hint of warming chili and cinnamon.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$17.00</p>\n                    <button class=\"add-to-cart\">Add to Cart</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" style=\"margin-top: 50px;\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">At Gourmet Chocolate Delights, we are passionate about the art of chocolate making. We source the finest cocoa beans from around the world and meticulously craft each piece to bring you an unforgettable sensory journey. Our commitment to quality and flavour is in every bite.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" style=\"margin-top: 50px;\">\n            <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Have questions or custom order inquiries? Reach out to us!</p>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Email: info@gourmetchocolatedelights.com</p>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Phone: (123) 456-7890</p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Gourmet Chocolate Delights. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelectorAll('.add-to-cart').forEach(button => {\n            button.addEventListener('click', function() {\n                alert('Item added to your cart!');\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}